description:
Super AMOLED brings colors to life
See every color and detail come alive on the 6.5-inch FHD+ Super AMOLED display. Enjoy crystal-clear visibility in shows and streams with 1,000 nits of brightness. Plus, with enhanced blue light protection, you can comfortably watch your content day or night.
Simple yet stylish
Experience a modern take on a classic look with a glossy finish. Choose a color that reflects your style. Available in Black, Dark Red, Light Green or Silver.
Snap and share your special moments
From portraits to wide-angle shots, snap every side of your world. Capture broad landscapes with the Ultra Wide camera and get close to tiny details with the Macro camera. Reduce blur in your photos and videos with OIS on the 50MP Main camera and take true-to-life selfies with the 13MP Front camera.
Speed up your routine with octa-core
Enjoy seamless scrolling and streaming with the powerful octa-core processor. Do more and see more in less time with the speed you need.
Experience the freedom of space
Take advantage of the ample 128GB storage space. Better yet, with up to 1TB additional storage on a microSD card, you can worry less about running out of space.
A battery to handle your days of fun
Stream, post and share with a 5,000mAh (typical) battery that lasts more than 2 days on a single charge.
